  <brief_title>Trial of Techniques for Umbilical Reconstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Umbilicoplasty: A Randomized Controlled Trial of Techniques for Umbilical Reconstruction Following Abdominoplasty and Abdominally-based Free Tissue Transfer</official_title>
